originalText.text: Dr Weiser-McCarthy is a gift. She is thoroughly knowledgeable, very intuitive, and incredibly warm and caring. Not only did she discover an underlying health issue my previous doctors had missed for years, but she follows up with what feels like sincere care. She treats the whole patient with a 360-degree perspective, and recognizes the benefits of nutrition and meditation, which I appreciate. I have found such thoughtfulness, time, and attention to be rare among doctors in NYC.

originalText.text: Dr. Jessica Weiser-MCarthy is a fantastic doctor: thorough, intelligent, caring and professional. She spends so much time and attention with every patient at every visit.
